title: 6: Stiff Socks Eats 1,300 Calorie Ice Cream Burrito
itunes:title: Stiff Socks Eats 1,300 Calorie Ice Cream Burrito
description:
Stiff Socks goes to the #1 ice cream shop in LA and tries to eat a HUGE ice cream burrito. They learn that a cotton candy tortilla is actually amazing but running after eating a cotton candy tortilla is not.
